{"tid":705102,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[子華]魚蛋論真實版","createTime":"2018-06-16T23:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T21:29:58.000Z","uid":107572,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc163ab479bd5176eef1510ab8427b37ab16bdcc","tid":705102,"uid":107572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:09:53.000Z","msg":"今日去葵芳嗰間麻辣川米線食米線我叫咗兩個餸，肥牛九蚊，餃子六蚊，個 friend 淨係叫咗一個餸，六蚊餃子。兩碗米線送到過嚟，個 friend 有4粒米線，我嗰碗得2粒餃。問個 waiter 係咪俾少咗，佢竟然話唔係，如果叫一個餸就係俾4粒，2個餸就2粒。我話我都係俾咁多錢喎，點解人哋有4粒我得2粒？嗰條友竟然同我講話不嬲廚房都係咁出，然後頭也不回走咗去。即係點？歧視我大食？屌你老母以後唔撚會再幫襯呢間嘢。"},{"pid":"72e1dffde4f3651f7506ba3bd29ae7c8259d1c3a","tid":705102,"uid":159518,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"譚仔都係，一餸永遠最抵食"},{"pid":"ea6580e13e8e2bca384df731d7e94769be9d946a","tid":705102,"uid":95499,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:21:12.000Z","msg":"4粒米線咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee260b961f134998d59a8fffe0f0e50b62db0338","tid":705102,"uid":107572,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea6580e13e8e2bca384df731d7e94769be9d946a","tid":705102,"uid":95499,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:21:12.000Z","msg":"4粒米線咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:24:36.000Z","msg":"打錯，4粒餃"},{"pid":"45fbc397231dec3564cf2fd6210e4de1be82abe4","tid":705102,"uid":107572,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"72e1dffde4f3651f7506ba3bd29ae7c8259d1c3a","tid":705102,"uid":159518,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"譚仔都係，一餸永遠最抵食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:28:06.000Z","msg":"完全唔明，食燒味飯加四蚊單拼變雙拼你每樣餸俾少啲咁講得通，家下我俾完全一樣嘅價錢，點解要俾少啲我？都痴撚線。"},{"pid":"6f11fc8d65aca5d6bbab3be54fd678e2e66e476f","tid":705102,"uid":68132,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T23:35:46.000Z","msg":"車仔麵形式嘅話應